#

Spicy Black Bean Soup

40 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh FiberGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupEasyHealthy

Description

A hearty and flavorful soup packed with protein and spices, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • canned black beans: 2 cans
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • diced tomatoes: 1 can
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • bell pepper: 1 medium, chopped
  • corn: 1 cup, frozen or canned
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
  • cayenne pepper: to taste
